Package io.github.eutro.wasm2j

Class ModuleAdapter

java.lang.Object
io.github.eutro.jwasm.BaseVisitor<ModuleVisitor>
io.github.eutro.jwasm.ModuleVisitor
io.github.eutro.wasm2j.ModuleAdapter
public class ModuleAdapter extends ModuleVisitor
An ModuleVisitor that adapts a WebAssembly module into a Java class, such that it can accept(org.objectweb.asm.ClassVisitor) an ObjectWeb ASM ClassVisitor.
